"8b678135d3e878e1fb7f8d1863a6d0adfadac1e4","tid":318802,"uid":24381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會難上手好多，睇你係唔係真心有興趣</blockquote><br />\n有興趣呀，但我驚連睇都唔明，仲點興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227d4d9d64eac8067afc2481f5ee2c0809d1a600","tid":318802,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"你要預左每份功課都要睇一大堆英文journal同埋寫一大堆英文"},{"pid":"2b2280cb597e1a04baf7c31b932950cfcc3952af","tid":318802,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會難上手好多，睇你係唔係真心有興趣</blockquote><br />\n有興趣呀，但我驚連睇都唔明，仲點興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你試下求其搵篇journal睇下先 睇下多唔多唔明"},{"pid":"d6eee2901a5fa9d353474bbc01e3249e1c5dddd2","tid":318802,"uid":35666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"出來打算做咩？我識幾個人讀心理出來都唔係做心理！<br />\n做心理要有master 先有用"},{"pid":"faa19b0f766ebb718eee906f94acb2059be1ba35","tid":318802,"uid":101169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg&h=a0de5653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到中間開始唔明係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a079ade9e824fd5f02861815e4348711616d00","tid":318802,"uid":125939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg&h=a0de5653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到中間開始唔明係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少事，只係睇唔明專有名詞，查個字典就明嫁啦"},{"pid":"825cd829707d0d130ca7a54da133fc5e7a082bb3","tid":318802,"uid":101169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg&h=a0de5653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到中間開始唔明係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少事，只係睇唔明專有名詞，查個字典就明嫁啦</blockquote><br />\nD專有名詞係咪查普通英漢字典就得？定有d心理學專有字典?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe81603a67387f0eea86c884973aea4efd49ce8","tid":318802,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"心理學既jargons同journals仲有psychometric test樣樣都係英文，底唔好真係咪讀，你會後悔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你問下自己，有冇能力為一份功課睇20份jounrals同埋參考書。英文基本功穩陣既話連埋寫其實一日內已經搞掂。<br />\n然後就係fyp自己寫份proposal比大學睇，approve你先有得做，但講緊未落筆寫fyp，剩係份proposal你都要預左分分鐘寫過萬字，比其他功課睇多幾倍jounrals咁。你要讀就做好心理準備。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：英文底子好既過來人"},{"pid":"058976f2788dc805848747b9c87d907991dd721a","tid":318802,"uid":125939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F195524_e3b2955f97ba4d0d9d13c12120df90f2.jpg&h=a0de5653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到中間開始唔明係咪人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少事，只係睇唔明專有名詞，查個字典就明嫁啦</blockquote><br />\nD專有名詞係咪查普通英漢字典就得？定有d心理學專有字典?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知喎，不過我睇呢篇文見到&quot;experiential avoidance&quot; , 查字典會查到 「體驗避免」，你唔會明佢講咩； 係google 打 &quot;experiential avoidance 心理學&rdquo; 就會知佢其實係一種迴避痛苦嘅現象，為避免厭惡經驗而採取不良措施去改變事件嘅頻率 類似「一朝被蛇咬十年怕草繩」"},{"pid":"8bd6646e8ec4ff0d1b22fcdea722ea13c81714a3","tid":318802,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbc1926c7c6babac7e2ead3d15e4d97c8a45940","tid":318802,"uid":124115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:28:40.000Z","msg":"你問下自己讀吾讀到上master先la<br />\n吾係master=乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0061a4ca74304f6d720102ded06f904708582879","tid":318802,"uid":16707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你問下自己讀吾讀到上master先la<br />\n吾係master=乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}